title: Princess Ella Soft vs Grunge
description: Princess Ella is looking for her own unique style. She tries out a new style called Soft. Representatives of the soft girl subculture prefer comfortable and soft clothes. The makeup is dominated by pink and peach shades. The entire aesthetics of the style is literally imbued with emotionality and sensuality, kindness and tenderness. Rainbow prints, drawings in the form of hearts, stars, bears, clouds are welcome. There are many childish elements in the aesthetics. The grunge style is the exact opposite of the soft style.
